name: Madelyn Cline
description:
Madelyn Renee Cline (born December 21, 1997) is an American actress and model. She is known for her roles as Sarah Cameron on the Netflix teen drama series Outer Banks (2020–present) and as Whiskey in Rian Johnson's mystery film Glass Onion: A Knives Out Mystery (2022).

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

Hello everyone! Today I present to you my textual inversion of Madelyn Cline! I used 50 public images of her with a 7000 steps process. To use it in your works:

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • add madclyne97 to your prompt;

  • keep the sampling steps around 20/25, and CFG between 7 and 8 to work well. Great results with DPM++ SDE Karras & Edge of Realism;
